is run by the Communist Party.

39
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:13,910
So unsurprisingly, Christmas is not a particularly
religious holiday in China.

40
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:18,739
But it has recently become China's second-biggest
holiday, after Chinese New Year.

41
00:02:18,739 --> 00:02:22,520
